ИLaughter, sunshine, first football kick with Daddy, and love
bigger thank this park. Let these ingredients of childhood
happiness always stay with you. For our boys, Yuli and Ilya
grandparents, Galina and Valery Vasiliev. May 2011"П
МIn Loving Memory of
Michael & Bridget Gannon
Forever in our Hearts
Moisan Family
xxxxxx

Those you love don't go away.
They walk beside you every day.
Unseen, unheard, but always near.
Still loved, still missed, still very dear."С
ПTim Slane walked these Battersea paths all his life
drawing solace & inspiration from this oasis.
Rest here and see what he saw, look up & see the canopy
& the life in it, making its way as he did
Sadly missed. Tim Slane, 58 years young"С
